    "Figure 6 in main text, and S8 for the same model and a different answer generation strategy).",
    "In order to assess the robustness of our results based on the prompting strategy, we tested different approaches.",
    "To this effect, we ran an experience on the US data with GPT-4 Turbo, testing three different prompting strategies.",
    "The interview one is the one presented above, in the text (section \"Generated data: Surveying a large language model\").",
    "The chat approach is the same as the interview one, except that the question-answer pairs are fed to the model in the specific \"chat\" format used by chat assistants, instead of writing all the context variables as a single text block."
